options.text: I'm in search of a quest.
What do you know about the Imcando dwarves?
Do you have anything to trade?

8058be8d-d8d2-4b63-a39c-f4003c654c5f.title: <player>
8058be8d-d8d2-4b63-a39c-f4003c654c5f.text: What do you know about the Imcando dwarves?

89264a09-d5bf-476d-b71d-f96f4bbfb8d4.title: Reldo
89264a09-d5bf-476d-b71d-f96f4bbfb8d4.text:
Ah yes... for many hundreds of years they were the
world's most skilled smiths. They used secret smithing
knowledge passed down from generation to generation.

d36278da-96be-4bcd-a547-af7e94423dac.title: Reldo
d36278da-96be-4bcd-a547-af7e94423dac.text:
Unfortunately, about a century ago, the once thriving
race was wiped out during the barbarian invasions of
that time.

00f65bfb-ef58-4512-a035-0744e12ab54c.title: <player>
00f65bfb-ef58-4512-a035-0744e12ab54c.text: So are there any Imcando left at all?

15475119-7a18-4f50-97cb-0b06d256c07b.title: Reldo
15475119-7a18-4f50-97cb-0b06d256c07b.text:
I believe a few of them survived, but with the bulk of
their population destroyed their numbers have dwindled
even further.

73c54a36-4ed5-4dc2-9ad8-74d9c99a2872.title: Reldo
73c54a36-4ed5-4dc2-9ad8-74d9c99a2872.text:
They tend to keep to themselves, and they tend not to
tell people they're descendants of the Imcando, which is
why people think the tribe is extinct. However...

62ad9c48-027e-447e-9f7b-381110918220.title: Reldo
62ad9c48-027e-447e-9f7b-381110918220.text:
... you could try taking them some redberry pie. They
REALLY like redberry pie. I believe I remember a
couple living in Asgarnia near the cliffs on the
Asgarnian southern peninsula.

b46ab1f5-125e-486d-900e-602330a9ccbe.title: <player>
b46ab1f5-125e-486d-900e-602330a9ccbe.text: Ah. That's why you're in the library then.

54389f34-78f4-461f-962d-22edcccc7a68.title: Reldo
54389f34-78f4-461f-962d-22edcccc7a68.text:
Although I would probably be in here even if I didn't
work here. I like reading. Someday I hope to catalogue
all of the information stored in these books so all may
read it.

fe8f939f-c00d-4193-9120-bee2666207bd.title: <player>
fe8f939f-c00d-4193-9120-bee2666207bd.text: Do you have anything to trade?

dd70e471-6f58-4951-b21f-ead45fbdd3c9.title: <player>
dd70e471-6f58-4951-b21f-ead45fbdd3c9.text: How much do you want for that then?

8614fe78-4c6b-4017-a081-39a5a0cfcdf8.title: Reldo
8614fe78-4c6b-4017-a081-39a5a0cfcdf8.text:
No, sorry, that was just my little joke. I'm not the
trading type.
